ay</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/playing_event\"><code>playing</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/progress_event\"><code>progress</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/ratechange_event\"><code>ratechange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/seeked_event\"><code>seeked</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/seeking_event\"><code>seeking</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/stalled_event\"><code>stalled</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/suspend_event\"><code>suspend</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/timeupdate_event\"><code>timeupdate</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/volumechange_event\"><code>volumechange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/waiting_event\"><code>waiting</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>当暂停媒体播放时 <code>pause</code> 事件触发， 并且媒体进入暂停状态，最常见的是通过<code>pause()</code>方法来触发。 当<code>pause()</code> 触发时<code>pause</code>状态只改变 1 次，并且媒体的<code>pause</code>变成 <code>true</code>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"general_info","title":"General info","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Bubbles</th>\n      <td>No</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Cancelable</th>\n      <td>No</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Interface</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Target</th>\n      <td>Element</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Default Action</th>\n      <td>None</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Event handler property</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/pause_event\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers.onpause</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Specification</th>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.whatwg.org/specs/web-apps/current-work/multipage/the-video-element.html#event-media-playing\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5 media</a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下面例子给媒体添加 <code>pause</code> 事件监听 handler，然后事件发生时会给 handler 发送一个提醒信息</p>\n<p>使用 <code>addEventListener()：</code></p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> video <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'video'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nvideo<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'pause'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'The Boolean paused property is now true. Either the '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">'pause() method was called or the autoplay attribute was toggled.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>使用 <code>onpause</code> 事件监听属性：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> video <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'video'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nvideo<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onpause</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'The Boolean paused property is now true. Either the '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">'pause() method was called or the autoplay attribute was toggled.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/media.html#event-media-pause","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.HTMLMediaElement.pause_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLMediaElement.pause_event","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/pause_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关事件","title":"相关事件","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/playing_event\" title=\"HTMLMediaElement: playing event\"><code>HTMLMediaElement: playing event</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/waiting_event\"><code>HTMLMediaElement: waiting event</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/seeking_event\"><code>HTMLMediaElement: seeking event</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/seeked_event\"><code>HTMLMediaElement: seeked event</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/ended_event\" title=\"HTMLMediaElement: 